<plot>Faye and Charlie are 2 friends having a common conversation, 'Would you rob a bank, and if you would, how would you do it?' Using people in the hookah bar as examples in their hypothetical situation, they play out a few details to plan the perfect robbery. Once Charlie decides on a costume he plays out the situation from start to finish. Faye acts as crowd control during the final robbery and points out Charlie's faults in his plan. This short was done as one single take to show the blur between fantasy and reality in this otherwise everyday situation.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?245126</url></doc>
